---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - WHEELS AI">
  <div class="legal-container content-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <section>
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using WHEELS AI, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our service.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Service Description</h2>
      <p>WHEELS AI provides AI-powered wheel visualization and customization services. We offer both free trials and premium subscriptions with varying features and limitations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. User Accounts</h2>
      <p>To access certain features, you must create an account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account information and for all activities under your account.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Credits and Payment</h2>
      <p>Free trial accounts receive 80 credits. Premium subscriptions include additional credits and features. All payments are processed securely through our payment provider.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All generated designs remain your intellectual property. However, WHEELS AI retains rights to the underlying technology and algorithms used to generate the designs.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Usage Guidelines</h2>
      <p>Users agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Attempt to bypass system limitations</li>
        <li>Share account access with unauthorized users</li>
        <li>Use the service for illegal purposes</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer the platform</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Modifications</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of modified terms.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="last-updated">
      Last updated: January 2024
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-container {
    padding-top: calc(var(--navbar-height) + var(--content-top-padding) + 4rem);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(245, 245, 240, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 245, 240, 0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(245, 245, 240, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
